Bantamweight Bethe Correia tsohuwar 'yar wasan damben UFC ce amma ta yi kuskure mai son yin hakan ta hanyar juya akalarta ga abokin karawarta Pannie Kianzad da kuma kuskuren tunanin cewa zagayen ya kare a fadan da suka yi a tsibirin Fight Island, kuma sun samu tagged a sakamakon haka.
